snippet.title: Warranty Not Include (WNI) - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming January 15th 2025!
💥 Join the Resistance Now! 💥
Warranty Not Included is a fun and accessible VR shooter perfect for newcomers. Practice your aim in various ranges and blast away at hordes of robotic enemies. 

Links:
🎮 Wish list on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3012350/Warranty_Not_Included/
💬 Join the Official WNI Discord: https://discord.com/invite/caVGQxAVjx
🌐 View Webpage: https://production.vrxtra.com/

Don’t miss out - gear up and save the future!
